 as needed.\\n\\nA few things to adjust once the project fills out:\\n\\n- **Node version** -- currently pinned to `22.x`. Change in the `matrix.node-version` array if you need multi-version testing.\\n- **Test runner** -- `node --test` works for built-in tests. If you use Vitest, change `\\\"test\\\": \\\"vitest run\\\"` and add it as a dev dep.\\n- **ESLint config** -- add `eslint.config.js` (flat config) or `.eslintrc.json` to make lint actually do something.\\n- **`npm ci`** -- requires a `package-lock.json` committed to the repo. Run `npm install` locally first to generate it.\\n\",\"numLines\":16,\"startLine\":1,\"totalLines\":16}}}\n21\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"350278b0-fbd7-40a0-ac15-228a8d68c51f","uuid":"a8032ecf-3b85-4548-b3a8-4dc98d091658","timestamp":"2026-04-28T20:00:21.065Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"C:\\Users\\LarsGyrupBrinkNielse\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\lz-advisor-def-kra8\\E-output.jsonl","content":"{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"hook_started\",\"hook_id\":\"f809ff08-5fca-47be-9b24-668e63d01eb0\",\"hook_name\":\"SessionStart:startup\",\"hook_event\":\"SessionStart\",\"uuid\":\"f6ebc3a8-b0ee-4e5a-9f8e-d156a2a779a5\",\"session_id\":\"350278b0-fbd7-40a0-ac15-228a8d68c51f\"}\n{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"hook_started\",\"hook_id\":\"2d37f66a-fd73-47ab-a4f1-287116b3bcb9\",\"hook_name\":\"SessionStart:startup\",\"hook_event\":\"SessionStart\",\"uuid\":\"dd0b5722-663a-4f9c-ac96-a93ef6100c23\",\"session_id\":\"350278b0-fbd7-40a0-ac15-228a8d68c51f\"}\n{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"hook_response\",\"hook_id\":\"2d37f66a-fd73-47ab-a4f1-287116b3bcb9\",\"hook_name\":\"SessionStart:startup\",\"hook_event\":\"SessionStart\",\"output\":\"\",\"stdout\":\"\",\"stderr\":\"\",\"exit_code\":0,\"outcome\":\"success\",\"uuid\":\"e292de62-7545-4a88-8c16-6cac2accb9e7\",\"session_id\":\"350278b0-fbd7-40a0-ac15-228a8d68c51f\"}\n{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"hook_response\",\"hook_id\":\"f809ff08-5fca-47be-9b24-